data.description: REMARKABLE 6 BEDROOM, 4.5 BATH POOL HOME IN THE HEART OF FRUITLAND PARK with a LAKE VIEW!!! Over 4000 Square feet of Heated and Cooled Living Space plus a 3 CAR GARAGE! Beautiful Pool & Spa area with Gorgeous Pavers and a Screened Lanai. This home has had so many recent updates including Newly Painted Exterior, New Roof in 2018, New AC's (yes both of them ) in 2018, Reme-Halo Air Purifiers recently installed, Pool was resurfaced in 2018, New Hardwood Laminate Floors , New Carpet downstairs, new lightfixture/ceiling fans plus more details that you will love. On the first floor you will find an inviting space with the new wood floors and plenty of cabinets in the kitchen along with gorgeous Corian Countertops and NEW Stainless Steel Appliances. The first floor also features a huge living room, a bedroom with a full bath and a half bath for your guests because this is the perfect house for entertaining. On the second floor you will find 4 guest bedrooms , loft space , 3 guest baths and a huge huge huge master along with a very spacious master bath. Come sip your coffee on the amazing pool lanai while overlooking the magnificent lake view!! You must see to belive so schedule your private showing today.
